    · refine ⟨2, 2, 2, ⟨by norm_num, by norm_num, by norm_num⟩, ⟨by norm_num, by norm_num⟩, ⟨1, by norm_num⟩, ⟨1, by norm_num⟩, ⟨1, by norm_num⟩, ⟨rfl, rfl, rfl⟩⟩
